== Kongregate's butthurt ==
After CocoaPuff310 had asked, on him own accord, to be [[B&|banned]] from [http://www.kongregate.com/| Kongregate] and then not being banned for being underage, members of Kongregate erupted in a shit-fit of whether or not he should be banned. Of course this was caught by [http://www.kongregate.com/accounts/ritzfitz91| one member] who came in and successfully [[Troll|calmed]] the [[Butthurt|butthurt]] Kongregate members. In the end the thread was found to be entirely useless, possibly even [[Lulzy|full of lulz]] for CocoaPuff310.


